[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "真正进入城市中心后，哪怕是浓雾也再无法掩盖这里的混乱……不，应该用天崩地裂来形容。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一幢又一幢的建筑被拦腰折断，横陈在路面上。立交桥与路面设施同样无法幸免，几乎已经是沟壑纵横。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "尤为诡异的是，在我前进的同时，对这座城市的破坏仍然在继续。时不时便会有建筑在我的眼前倒塌，而我却完全看不到攻击这些建筑的人。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "它们像是遭到了另一个次元的攻击，会毫无征兆地崩裂开来。这严重迟缓了我前进的速度，不仅需要躲避坍塌，还要在废墟中找到可供通行的道路。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "唯一一个不知道算不算得上好消息的情况是，这些来源不明的攻击唯独避开了我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "有那么几次，我分明与被攻击的大楼完全重合，却毫发无伤地躲过了攻击。所以我才能够不用去躲避未知的攻击，而只需要应付攻击所带来的次生危害。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但另一方面，我几乎可以肯定，对城市的攻击与恩雅有关。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我只得不断加快步伐，并利用泰坦物质外壳护住要害，在倒塌的楼宇之间上下穿行。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不知过了多久，当我最终抵达城市中心时，出现在眼前的景象，已经与数小时前截然不同。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这里的雾已经完全散去，而上百幢倒塌的大楼所环绕着的城市中心，赫然成为了一块巨大的空地。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "建筑被削去，沟壑被填平，只留下灰白色的平整地面——一个巨大而完美的圆。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我站在边缘一幢损毁大楼的顶端，从脚下的颤动中感受着从空地中央传来的力量。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这份力量犹如心脏搏动，平稳地向着四周扩散出去，所到之处便会产生猛烈的震动。我能够想象出，这个巨大的圆正是由这一次次的扩散形成。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我也终于能够看清，在圆的中心，突兀地存在着圆内唯一的建筑。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那是一幢我不久前才见过的小木屋。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我不再犹豫，大步朝着木屋冲去。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "轰……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "圆外的建筑被不明的力量冲击着，仍然在不断倒塌，发出震耳欲聋的声音。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但对于置身于圆内的我来说，这股力量像是不存在，无法——似乎也不愿阻止我的前进。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我的步伐不断加快，最终与那扩散的能量节奏重合。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "有那么一瞬间，一个模糊的人影出现在了空地之上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而在捕捉到她的时刻，我冲向了她。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "此刻，两个重叠的世界不过一线之隔，而现在，我已经触碰到了那条线。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "周围的一切骤然发生了变化。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "无法驱散的浓雾不断上升，变成了积压着黯色的雨云，在城市上空降下淅淅沥沥的小雨。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "被碾为齑粉的高楼大厦重新拔地而起，遮蔽了大半天空。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "只有我所处的地方，仍然存在着一片空地，虽然已经比现实中小了许多。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但那些都不重要了。对我来说最重要的是，恩雅，就站在离我不远的地方。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "思索清楚现状前，身体已经先一步做出了反应。我箭步上前，堪堪为恩雅挡下了一记扑面而来的能量攻击。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "轰！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "发生在眼前的爆炸将我震退了半步，但在泰坦物质护甲的保护之下，我并没有受到什么伤害。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "看来，是赶上了啊。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我回过头去，对恩雅露出一个微笑。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_girl011_01",
        "zh_CN": "分析员……！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "少女的脸上带着仍未退去的惊讶，原本紧绷着的身体却立刻放松下来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "恩雅，我很想现在就让你抱一下，但是……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一边说着，我一边伸出手去，再次挡下了一记攻击。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就现在的情况来说，可能需要等等了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_girl011_02",
        "zh_CN": "真是的……现在也要耍帅吗，哥哥大人？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她露出笑容，随手擦掉了脸颊上的汗珠，将头发捋到耳后，然后快步来到了我的身旁。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_girl011_03",
        "zh_CN": "太好了，你没事……真是太好了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我能感觉到她正强忍着激动的心情，以至于声音都有些微微颤抖。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我没事，倒是你这边发生了什么？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_girl011_04",
        "zh_CN": "简单来说，我和对面那个意识体说你会来找我，它不相信，所以我们打起来了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她的玩笑中带着炫耀，看起来她并没有因为对方的攻击而受伤。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我循着恩雅的目光看去，果然在远处看到了一个模糊的人影，那些破坏力惊人的能量也正是从它的身上直射而出。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_girl011_05",
        "zh_CN": "它……或者说它们，自称是16区的意识。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "所以说，我在吸收那个光团的时候，看到的城市毁灭的画面，就是来自于这个意识体的记忆吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_girl011_06",
        "zh_CN": "嗯，我想应该就是这样。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_girl011_07",
        "zh_CN": "这个意识体中充斥着悲伤和痛苦的信息，那些信息形成了16区里种种异象，也就是莉琪所说的模因集合体。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我思索着恩雅的话，忽然感觉脑中的逻辑链条逐渐连接起来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "归根结底，16区不可能凭空产生出集体意识，我之前的猜测应该是对的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_girl011_08",
        "zh_CN": "什么猜测？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "关于幕后黑手。很显然，16区一切的异常都是有人促成的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那个人将16区里的信息态融合在一起，让这座城市变得像“树”一样，能够不断吸收附近的意识。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_girl011_09",
        "zh_CN": "分析员的意思是，这是埃达的计划吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不，对方更像是在模仿埃达。而且，16区作为一个被军方管控的前隔离区，很少会有人进入，这并不符合埃达的目的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 58,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "说到这里，我已经隐约有了眉目。似乎像是听到了我和恩雅的交谈，16区意识体的攻击也慢慢停了下来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 59,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我和恩雅随即向前走去，靠近到了离对方十米左右的位置。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 60,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "能和我聊聊吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 61,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我平静地注视着这个由能量构成的人影，对方并未作答，像是默认了我的提问。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 62,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我想知道，你们的目的是什么？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 63,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "16区",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_area16_01",
        "zh_CN": "<red>解脱。</>",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 64,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "简短的两个字出现在我的眼前，却像是带着千斤的重量。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 65,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "16区",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_area16_02",
        "zh_CN": "<red>意识的存在，本身就意味着痛苦。</>",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 66,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "16区",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_area16_03",
        "zh_CN": "<red>从我们的意识诞生开始，我们就在不断吸收城市中的同类。而吸收得越多，痛苦与悲伤就越多。</>",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 67,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "16区",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_area16_04",
        "zh_CN": "<red>我们已经在这痛苦中挣扎了太久，而且永远没有尽头。</>",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 68,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "16区",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_area16_05",
        "zh_CN": "<red>既然如此，我们想要帮助你们解脱。</>",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 69,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我又一次想起了埃达，无论是被“树”吸收，还是被意识体吞噬，它们似乎都认为这是让人类得到所谓的“救赎”的方法。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 70,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_girl011_10",
        "zh_CN": "存在或许会带来痛苦，但爱与希望也同样会从中诞生，不是吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 71,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "16区",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_area16_06",
        "zh_CN": "<red>……</>",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 72,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "16区",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_area16_07",
        "zh_CN": "<red>对于我们来说，在城市毁灭的那一天，就已经只剩下痛苦。</>",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 73,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "16区",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_area16_08",
        "zh_CN": "<red>但是，不知道为什么，你们不一样。</>",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 74,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我感觉意识体“看向”了我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 75,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "16区",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_area16_09",
        "zh_CN": "<red>你不仅接触，甚至吸收了我们的痛苦，却并没有因此崩溃。</>",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 76,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "16区",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_area16_10",
        "zh_CN": "<red>你的坚韧胜过任何人，甚至让我们感到……敬畏。</>",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 77,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "16区",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_area16_11",
        "zh_CN": "<red>而另一个，我们仍然不理解，为什么你触碰到了那些痛苦，却完全没有受到影响。</>",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 78,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我看向恩雅，她则摇了摇头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 79,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_girl011_11",
        "zh_CN": "它们让我看到了分析员处在痛苦之中，所以我触碰了那股能量。除此之外，我并没有做什么特别的事情。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 80,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "原来如此……那个时候是恩雅保护了我的意识，让我从中脱离出来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 81,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我露出释然的微笑，转而看向远处的意识体。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 82,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这样的话，理由很简单，因为恩雅就是恩雅。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 83,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "总是能很快理解其他人，不愿意让任何无辜的人陷入痛苦中，保护别人的时候总是奋不顾身，对待恶人也从不会手下留情。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 84,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她是特别的，是心中没有阴影的人。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 85,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "16区",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_area16_12",
        "zh_CN": "<red>心中……没有阴影？</>",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 86,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我抚上恩雅的脸颊，因为我的话语，她的脸正微微发烫，浮现出漂亮的红晕。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 87,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "遇到恩雅之前，我也不相信世界上真的有这样的人。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 88,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但既然世界上有着纯粹的恶人，那真正善良无瑕的人也应该存在。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 89,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "看吧，她已经证明过了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 90,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_girl011_12",
        "zh_CN": "分析员，我……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 91,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "恩雅语无伦次地想说些什么，我则抓紧了她的手，让她不用抑制住心中的感情。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 92,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我想让你们相信，从痛苦中解脱出来的方法，一定是存在的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 93,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "16区",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_area16_13",
        "zh_CN": "<red>……</>",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 94,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我看着16区的意识体产生了些许波动，从人形变成了一个漩涡状的光团。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 95,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "16区",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_area16_14",
        "zh_CN": "<red>谢谢你们。</>",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 96,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "16区",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_area16_15",
        "zh_CN": "<red>如果早些遇到你们，也许情况就不会变成这样。</>",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 97,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "16区",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_area16_16",
        "zh_CN": "<red>但是，已经来不及了。现在，除了战斗之外别无他法。</>",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 98,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "光团中的能量陡然增加了许多，几乎将天空也照得澄亮。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 99,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但与此同时，城市中的其他地方变得愈发昏暗。建筑失去了色彩，雨滴落地的声音也被剥夺，16区里所有的信息都源源不断地汇聚到了意识体的身上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 100,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "哪怕还与它们相距十米，我却也已经感觉到了阴郁与绝望的气息。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 101,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "下一刻，一道道能量汇聚成躯体，成百上千的异化人出现在我们周围，如同浪潮般缓慢又不可阻挡地向我们靠近。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 102,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我和恩雅对视一眼，都从对方的眼中看出了些许犹豫。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 103,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "想要应对这些敌人并不困难，但我们都很清楚，眼前的每一个怪物都曾是16区里的一个意识。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 104,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "击倒它们的同时，意识集合体就会分出一部分能量，为它们提供新的生命力，让它们不断复生。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 105,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这样一来，只是对它们发起攻击的话，就始终无法彻底解决它们，只能为其带来更多痛苦。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 106,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在我思索的同时，恩雅已经制造出了风墙，将我们与敌人隔离开来。即使这样，它们依然不断靠近，前仆后继地冲击着这道屏障。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 107,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "眼看在一次又一次的冲击之下，恩雅明显已经有些体力不支，我走上前去，扶住了她的肩膀，对她点了点头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 108,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_girl011_13",
        "zh_CN": "分析员，是已经有办法了吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 109,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯，我想把我们之前做过的事情再做一遍。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 110,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "还记得吗？在那个时候，我们尝试过改变模因中的内容。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 111,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "以现在的情况而言，应该只有这个办法能平息那意识体的痛苦。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 112,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_girl011_14",
        "zh_CN": "我知道，但这样的话，分析员必须要吸收那些能量才行。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 113,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在之前或许很困难，但现在……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 114,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我抬起手，指向那些异化人。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 115,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "它们的意识分散在了单独的个体上，而不再是一个巨大的集体意识。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 116,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "如果是现在去逐个吸收这些意识的话，我应该能够支撑得住。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 117,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "恩雅看向我，动了动嘴唇，却没有发出声音。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 118,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "迟疑了片刻之后，她才重新抬起头来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 119,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_girl011_15",
        "zh_CN": "我相信分析员的判断，但是……除了维持这个风墙之外，我似乎也帮不到分析员了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 120,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不，我还需要恩雅的帮助。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 121,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_girl011_16",
        "zh_CN": "可我……应该做什么？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 122,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "让我感觉到恩雅的存在，让我在吸收那些痛苦和绝望的情绪的时候，提醒我，我的身边就存在着爱与希望。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 123,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我轻轻拨开她的发梢，在她的额头上留下一个吻。而她也不服输似的，踮起脚亲吻了我的额头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 124,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "当我们四目相对时，她的眼中透露着坚定的光芒。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 125,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_girl011_17",
        "zh_CN": "一直以来，我时常会觉得，自己缺少某种独特的力量。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 126,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_girl011_18",
        "zh_CN": "我没有能够过目不忘的才能，也没有掌握瞬间穿梭移动的能力。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 127,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_girl011_19",
        "zh_CN": "我没办法控制信息态制造幻象，在战斗上，也做不到最好。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 128,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_girl011_20",
        "zh_CN": "大概只有对分析员的爱，我有自信不会输给任何人。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 129,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_girl011_21",
        "zh_CN": "但是，分析员刚才告诉了我，恩雅就是恩雅。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 130,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_girl011_22",
        "zh_CN": "现在，能够有只有我才能做到的事情，我很开心。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 131,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_girl011_23",
        "zh_CN": "所以分析员，就放心去拯救那些痛苦的意识吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 132,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep5_girl011_24",
        "zh_CN": "我会一直在你的身边。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 133,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她抱住了我，紧紧贴近我的胸口，让我感觉到两颗心脏正以相同的频率跳动。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 134,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "与此同时，我也朝着风墙之外抬起了手。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 135,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "刹那间，16区的意识体接二连三地进入了我的脑海中。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 136,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我看到了将孩子护在身下的母亲，看到了只差一点就能赶上撤离的少女，看到了深入市区救助民众，却受伤濒死的士兵。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 137,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "千千万万个意识，发出同样痛苦的呼喊。这些意识都被困在生命最后的片段中，心中除了绝望别无它物。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 138,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在现实中，这些意识的结局早已注定，但在这里，我能够给每一个人一个希望。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 139,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在宛如地狱的城市中，我来到了一个又一个地方，朝着每一个人伸出了手。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 140,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "有的人只需要些许助力就能燃起希望，而有的人我几乎已经无力回天。在不断的尝试中，我的耳中充斥着哀嚎，让我几近力竭倒下。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 141,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但无论何时，当我回头看去，我都能看到一个身影。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 142,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她如同皎白的月亮，形影不离地跟随在我的身后，让我从痛苦中平复下来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 143,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我知道，她还在等待着我的好消息。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 144,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "最终，最后的意识也彻底消失，我的眼前只剩下残破而孤独的城市。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 145,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "16区，你又想成为什么呢？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 146,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我在心中如此默念着，旋即闭上了眼睛，向后倒去。",
